	  	<h3>Print sales</h3>
		<p>
			If you are interested in buying a physical print of my art I'm happy to say that I have an online <a href="/store">store</a>.<br><br>
			I print all my pieces myself and ships them from Mölndal to ensure that I have full control over the quality of my work. The prints are made using a high end printer, archival grade inks 
