			Shipping is included and the prints are shipped using PostNord as soon as the print is ready. 
			At this time I do not provide framing services for online orders due to the cost and difficulties of shipping framed items. 
			<br><br>

			If you have any questions regarding prints or ordering please write to <span>gallery@rahmn.net</span> or DM on <a class="normal" href="https://www.instagram.com/lukasrahmn/" >Instagram</a>
