		<h3>Returns</h3>
		<p>
			Prints are examined carefully before shipping for any quality issues. In the unfortunate event that you do receive a damaged or defective print I ask that you contact me and provide
			pictures of the damage. Such damaged prints will be replaced free of charge or refunded if unable to provide a new print. The exception to this is if damaged arose due to mishandling by the customer. <br><br>

			Do note that inkjet prints are very delicate by nature and should be handled by the edges to avoid scratching or thumbprints on the print surface. To ensure longevity of artwork I highly 
			recommend framing it behind glass or alternatively laminating it. If you have any questions regarding care or framing don't hesitate to contact me.<br><br>

			If you are unhappy with your print for any reasons you have the right to revoke the purchase within 14 days of receiving it. In such a case write to <span>gallery@rahmn.net</span>
			to arrange return and refund. In this case the return shipping cost is covered by the customer.<br><br>
		</p>


